<h3>Thieves</h3>

<ul>
    <li>Reveal 1 thief card</li>
    <li>When buying a Djinn, may instead buy a thief</li>
    <li>Tribe action <span class="arrow"></span> may activate & discard matching thief</li>
    <li>Cannot acquire & use thief on the same turn</li>
    <li>Effects that apply to Djinns do not apply to thieves</li>
    <li>Replenish thief card during cleanup</li>
</ul>

